data.description:
Beautiful Custom-built home original owner!Walk in to the Open Living/Kitchen/Dining to see many upgrades the home has to offer.The Kitchen is the centerpiece with SS Appliances, Workstation Sink, Induction Cooktop,Built-in Convection wall oven & Micro,42" wood cabinets with pullout drawers,Quartz Countertops,Walk-in Pantry, built-in swivel Bar chairs.Breakfast Nook and Formal Dining,currently used as a piano room.Split floorplan with the Primary in the back with a huge Bath & Walk-in Closet.The home has Trey ceilings with Crown molding,wood blinds,modern lighting and updated ceiling fans. There
are gorgeous wooden built-ins in the Office and GBR,18" Tile flooring & Carpeted BRooms.In house Utility Room with Storage.The front/back yards include Low Maintenance Landscaping with irrigation system.The backyard is your tropical oasis,complete with a large patio area with pergola,Inground Saltwater Pool w/Fountain&Lovely Landscaping! No need for a resort getaway when you have one
at home!
